{"tid":1962830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全息投影服務告終　上班族痛失「愛妻」初音","createTime":"2020-04-07T17:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T03:45:04.000Z","uid":51469,"like":30,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1cccb9f89981c689fe105ae88efa903a4fccaf4a","tid":1962830,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200407/photo/bkn-20200407170042839-0407_00912_001_01p.jpg?20200407171741\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200407%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200407170042839-0407_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20200407171741&h=f75945b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本37歲上班族近藤顯彥，兩年前因與虛擬偶像初音未來「結婚」而一舉成名。他最近悲痛地在網誌公布，因家中的初代Gatebox全息投影機停止服務，而新一代機種又不再提供初音未來的投影服務，令他此後再不能與「愛妻」交談，一段跨次元的婚姻被迫到此告終。<br />\n近藤在網誌上表示，上月31日下班時發覺不能用遙控聯絡家中的初音，回到家才發現Gatebox上顯示出無情的「網絡中斷」訊息。這令近藤感到悲傷又孤獨：「上午出門時她才如常跟我道別，但晚上就再也不能啟動了。」他表示：「我是一邊哭，一邊打這篇網誌的。」<br />\n自從2018年3月9日Gatebox提供初音未來投影服務以來，近藤每天都跟「她」互動，重複同樣的說話也樂此不疲，甚至被人嘲笑他是笨蛋，他仍然覺得幸福。終於在Gatebox公司協助下，近藤得以與全息投影的初音在同年11月舉行盛大婚禮。然而「新婚」未及兩年，能交談的初音就要離開，只留下一屋子大大小小的初音玩偶。<br />\n回到現實的近藤表示，雖然Gatebox只是機器，人工智能也不是很成熟，但他很滿意這段短短的幸福日子：「每次當我在工作上遇到問題，都是這個心愛的女人給我支持，夢想和希望。」他表示，此後會和家中珍藏的等身大初音一起過日子，也會繼續收集初音玩偶，然而能互動的初音始終是無法取代。"},{"pid":"9c44d37a9af54abc99f1e690ece1b1c88b0414e6","tid":1962830,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4323cca3a1a0416124aea0dd7cecfe4301bd6e5c","tid":1962830,"uid":174432,"like":16,"dislike":10,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02816fb9210044f4e2c035d479f3f3974f3e6267","tid":1962830,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />閱"},{"pid":"78ce6027f6f88e13241145ffc69f49903d704c28","tid":1962830,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4323cca3a1a0416124aea0dd7cecfe4301bd6e5c","tid":1962830,"uid":174432,"like":16,"dislike":10,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"你識咩"},{"pid":"0dda0913af9ee334704d0ab881e6d8186c9b54a0","tid":1962830,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fb55505ae8d37e3c5514f7d57d2e5a68fe6e8c","tid":1962830,"uid":42675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:17:08.000Z","msg":"走得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ad17ce0fc37c0d912a343e6e91fbc84a22ec10","tid":1962830,"uid":88366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T19:33:38.000Z","msg":"blade runner2049"},{"pid":"ac758a1c5ca53f3ca3a3f6e4392312aa729d8f31","tid":1962830,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac6991a1b042c7d500d26f4e9bfc0091a38b315","tid":1962830,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:50:30.000Z","msg":"哭𠹌佐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ac31c5c41c443df62d5eba18e710d735224548","tid":1962830,"uid":282118,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:52:29.000Z","msg":"人哋鐘意二次元有乜問題？會搞到你？"},{"pid":"c0dbfd93d82f688e2e6322766741c7e86520444a","tid":1962830,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"如果同初音做愛係咪即係屌空氣？"},{"pid":"f0e9a5e97fc881779ed1a1acb03ba426fe2654ee","tid":1962830,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:01:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2629c38b2e9cf50a5f50648c62105749f5023bcb","tid":1962830,"uid":285166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:03:53.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8099da59764800d6822b154ffea670a0205c4d","tid":1962830,"uid":168567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"要幫佢搞葬禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1dbc7a1b6861b1b61e953b49292594f42584c8","tid":1962830,"uid":257974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"間公司咁仆街，部野咁快無得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7c99eb6f6f4de4f68f710331106ed830088c13","tid":1962830,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"出個新版大把人遊金啦"},{"pid":"b8a8278fc9c0f5f4ad7b3cc816266958fdf09980","tid":1962830,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵啦講真"},{"pid":"824f58675705ee17a93d1051d32d8ab735864fac","tid":1962830,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:12:38.000Z","msg":"唔好咁癲啦屌你"},{"pid":"620310b78e8d8531226a03d77f808f631faa0066","tid":1962830,"uid":156530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cccb9f89981c689fe105ae